4", "card_id": "Q_392514169", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 191}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么明明《霍比特人》和《指环王》都是好结局，但是看完会很难受？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-18d7b2917280dce19aa6d966a35b82a0_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/392514169"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy52H987u7oVrEAMaCDQ5NTAzODU2INK6vvUFMAA4kwZAE3IJMzkyNTE0MTY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1775453124.736897", "card_id": "Q_658348543", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "985 和 211 的差距有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76ae20c2673d441d62e9ebf5129118bd_1440w.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&needBackground=1"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658348543"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy52H987u7oVrEAMaCTEwODU3NzcwOCCClIyzBjAAOF9AFHIJNjU4MzQ4NTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1775453124.737182", "card_id": "Q_2002191602567889161", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 446}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我们已知的所有规律都来自经验和推理，可是过去成立并不能推出未来也能一直成立，那么规律还可信吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我们现在知道的所有规律，都来自经验，即对过去的总结。例如我们知道东升西落，是因为我们观察了 N 次，每次的太阳都是东升西落的。例如我们知道水往低处流，也是我们观察了 N 次，发现水总是会自发的从高处流向低处。 可是过去成立的规律，并不能推出在将来也一定成立。例如你即使观察了十万次太阳的东升西落，你也不能保证太阳不会在第十万零一次从西边升起。例如你即使观察了一百万次水往低处流，你也不能保证水不会在第一百万零一次时自发的向高流。 虽然说现在有了物理学，很多自然规律都能用物理学知识来解释。可物理学的各种规律也都是来自经验和推理，如果经验不能保证永久成立，那么物理学理论也不能保证永久成立。你永远无法证明万有引力始终存在，你也无法证明 F＝ma 不会在某天变为 F＝a/m，你甚至无法保证物理学规律一定存在。或许在未来某一天，万有引力方向突然反转，于是「水往低处流」就变成了「水往高处流」，你无法证明不会发生这样的事情。 那么，在这个宇宙上，还有绝对正确的规律吗？所有根据经验总结出来的规律，真的绝对可信的吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c60291f046ee59392512529e92e5e006_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2002191602567889161"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIy52H987u7oVrEAMaCTExODMxNTM5NiCc4IjMBjAAOIMFQBVyEzIwMDIxOTE2MDI1Njc4ODkxNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1775453124.738151", "card_id": "Q_338097816", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "安东尼和德雷蒙德·格林，谁的历史地位更高？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一个是得分王，一个是冠军主力，在他们退役后，谁的历史地位会更高"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc777ea0be19808fffe97338fdbb7b45_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/338097816"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy52H987u7oVrEAMaCDM3NDA5NjczII2iieoFMAA4oAFAFnIJMzM4MDk3ODE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1775453124.738652", "card_id": "Q_1965560441464944190", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子 12 岁初二，基础薄弱导致成绩垫底，现在越学越没信心，甚至想辍学，家长该从哪一步开始帮他逆袭？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "孩子小学时成绩就中等偏下，当时没太重视，想着初中能跟上，结果初二课程难度一上来，数学、物理完全听不懂，作业基本靠抄，考试各科都在及格线边缘徘徊。现在他越来越自卑，说「再怎么学也赶不上」，放学回家就躲在房间玩手机，一提学习就发脾气，甚至跟我们说「不想上学了」。我们试过给他报补习班，但他上课坐不住、不配合，效果特别差；想帮他补基础，又不知道从哪科、哪个知识点入手，真的又焦虑又无助。有没有有类似经历的家长，或者教育方面的老师，能分享下具体的补救步骤？比如先抓哪科、怎么重建孩子的信心，还有适合基础薄弱孩子的学习方法？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c9b6358f51f2f2e6e84b349bf8dd8ddd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1965560441464944190"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIy52H987u7oVrEAMaCTExNzA4ODg2NiCv2fPHBjAAOFNAF3ITMTk2NTU2MDQ0MTQ2NDk0NDE5MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1775453124.739427", "card_id": "Q_507601009", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "韩国和越南过去用汉字，那时他们与我们能用汉字交流吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "能做何种程度的交流呢，类似粤语闽语纳西语还是日语这种，能否类比一下？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f874b2aa692e0787603b364a53599eac_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/507601009"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iy52H987u7oVrEAMaCDc1MDgxOTE1ILnCho4GMAA4bUAYcgk1MDc2MDEwMDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1775453124.739880", "card_id": "Q_2016068447918900691", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 87}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我被降薪 10%，经理说降薪总比被裁员好。结果他被降薪 20%，他就不干了，说自己负担重，该如何理解？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "朋友被降薪 10%，他们领导说：公司的政策，么有办法，降薪总比被裁员好。结果第二批降薪，他被降薪 20%，他就找公司去闹，说他不能接受，每月固定支出太多"}, "ima